burlap.domain.singleagent.gridworld

Class SerializableGridWorldStateFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.domain.singleagent.gridworld.SerializableGridWorldStateFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SerializableStateFactory

    public class SerializableGridWorldStateFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements SerializableStateFactory
    A factory for producing a simple SerializableState representation of GridWorldDomain states by using a string representation.
    String format:
    ax ay, l1x l1y l1t, l2x l2y lt2, ..., lnx lny lnt
    where ax and ay is the agent x and y position and lix liy is the ith location objects x and y position and lit is the type of the ith location object.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan.
